# Copy this file to `.env.local` if you want to provide a server-side fallback
# OpenAI API key. The app's Settings panel always takes precedence — users can
# paste their own key in the UI and it will be sent via the X-OpenAI-Key header
# on every request. Without either a settings key or this env var, AI features
# will return a 401 with a friendly "open Settings" message.

OPENAI_API_KEY=
